{"tid":2457391,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日 23號 星期二 14:30 上庭聲援熊仔餅呀 區 域 法 院８樓２７庭","createTime":"2021-03-22T14:58:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-22T23:36:08.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3b1d936faefbb2f289e6c02b4f6afa63c3371923","tid":2457391,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T14:58:31.000Z","msg":"聽日 23號 星期二 14:30 上庭聲援熊仔餅呀 區 域 法 院８樓２７庭<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n🏛區 域 法 院８樓２７庭<br />\n👨🏻&zwj;⚖️姚勳智法官<br />\n🕝14:30<br />\n👥周,胡(20-21) #提訊 (#1111西灣河 阻差辦公 企圖搶劫 企圖從合法羈押下逃脫)<br />\n👤*(14) #提訊 (#0831太子 非法集結 管有攻擊性武器)<br />\n<br />\n「熊仔餅」中槍夢魘 骨折、劇痛難久站  3.23上庭 盼手足聲援<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2382267\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2382267</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/XI4zEIdOWUNHfMw45vKPJMpurzY=/1794x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/2P7Y7A3DBBCLRNR7CEKJXQ4KH4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FXI4zEIdOWUNHfMw45vKPJMpurzY%3D%2F1794x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F2P7Y7A3DBBCLRNR7CEKJXQ4KH4.jpg&h=a5d8ac14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■前年11月，周柏均（右）遭警員近距離槍擊。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Ce42cM4IV1BaHKumGGIc7eZrQHU=/1000x563/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/O5XT4CCNOBCPHBUG7ITH4W6XTU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fre